  <span style="color: #f9a374;">Diagnostician</span>     <span style="color: #666;">diagnostic_analysis</span>            <span style="color: #555;">·</span>  <span style="color: #f9a374;">Pareto Analyst</span>    <span style="color: #666;">pareto_analysis</span>
