  <span style="color: #a78bfa;">Rule Suggester</span>    <span style="color: #666;">extract_business_rules</span>          <span style="color: #555;">·</span>  <span style="color: #a78bfa;">Chat Triple Extr</span>  <span style="color: #666;">extract_spo_triples</span>
